        <updateDate>2019-09-07T19:50:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Medicare Care Coordination Improvement Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill exempts certain alternative payment models under Medicare from the general prohibition on physician self-referrals (also known as the Stark law).<br /></p><br />]]></text>
      </summary>
